  <source>Cincinnati VA Medical Center</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the pilot study is to validate an assesment tool to be used in the assessment&#xD;
      of pain in the verbal, congitively intact patient. The ultimate goal is to be able to&#xD;
      validate this tool in the non-verbal/cognitively impaired patient.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patinets will be observed for 2 six hour periods. Patients will be videotaped; every 10&#xD;
      minutes: EMG reading will be obtained; hourly - vital signs, pain score and saliva cortisol&#xD;
      from &quot;spit&quot; will be obtained.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
